<br>
I have done some research.  I think that for the money, the three that I have listed sound the best.  I have looked up their speed/damage ratio and they are as follows:  (the lower the better)<br>
<br>
Polished Granite Tomahawk: 4.333<br>
<br>
Drakkel Forged Bastard Sword: 2.25<br>
<br>
Axe of the Ironback: 2.312<br>
<br>
The Drakkel has the best ratio.  However, many of you have said the PGT is really nice.  I know it has the beserker STR bonus when it kicks in.<br>
<br>
If anyone has an opinion about any of these, I'll greatly appreciate hearing about it.  And if any of you have one of these items for sale, please let me know.  I'd rather buy from guild members, than from strangers.<br>
<br>
Post, send a tell, or e-mail me.  Thanks.<br>
<br>
Your humble brother, <br>
~Kegdawen<br>
