<br>
I have played with rangers that go all out full bore.  They either end up dead or running in circles with a creature following them and it is absolute hell gettin the creatures off of said ranger and be able to kill it if you don't have a big nuke available.  So sometimes moderation is key.<br>
<br>
Just a thought... <p><HR><TABLE CELLSPACING=0 BORDER=0 CELLPADDING=7 WIDTH=375>
